Package: peakdistanceenrichment
Title: ATACseq or ChIPseq peak enrichment using a sliding distance
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given="James M.",
       family="Ward",
       email="jmw86069@gmail.com",
       comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-9510-2848"),
       role=c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: James M. Ward <jmw86069@gmail.com>
Description: Test ATACseq or ChIPseq genome regions (peaks) by
   hypergeometric enrichment with a set of genome features, 
   iterated across a sliding range of distances.
